# Runtime uploads — local-disk fallback for the upload paths that hit Azure
# blob storage in production. Patterns target the timestamp-/UUID-prefixed
# names the server generates, so committed default assets (avatar-NN.svg,
# party/venue/*.jpg, etc.) stay tracked.
public/assets/avatars/user-*
public/assets/party/[0-9]*-*
public/assets/products/
public/assets/content/
public/assets/responsive-screenshots/
